comments: Valentine (CHI) places a forearm against Gobert's (UTA) back and marginal contact occurs as he goes for the rebound.
Vucevic (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of O'Neale (UTA) and absorbs the contact.
O'Neale (UTA) collapses his arms and he braces for the ensuing marginal contact with Vucevic (CHI) in the post.
Williams (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the drive to the basket by Bogdanovic (UTA) and the contact with Bogdanovic's left arm is absorbed.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Conley (UTA).
Williams (CHI) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Vucevic (CHI) is never established in O'Neale's (UTA) path and he continues moving into him, delivering contact that affects his ability to defend the play.
Mitchell (UTA) makes incidental contact with Williams (CHI), who is behind him and attempts to reach for the rebound.
Vucevic (CHI) commits a take foul on O'Neale (UTA).
Gobert (UTA) places a resting arm against LaVine's (CHI) body and marginal contact occurs before he cleanly blocks the shot attempt at the rim.
